+Enables debug output to syslog(3). Equivalent to *loglevel*=_debug_ unless
+*loglevel* is also set, in which case *loglevel* takes precedence. See
+*LOGGING* below.
 
-*debug_file*::
-Filename to write debugging messages to. **If this file is missing,
